      <title>津巴布韦有望通过 ZiG 最终摆脱通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/with-zig-zimbabwe-expects-to-finally-turn-its-back-on-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦央行表示，新的黄金支持的ZiG货币将消除严重的通货膨胀，这种通货膨胀阻碍了经济，并使这个南部非洲国家成为物价压力失控的典范。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/with-zig-zimbabwe-expects-to-finally-turn-its-back-on-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:25:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
