    <item>
      <title>Challenger称美国公司四月份新员工数量减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/us-firms-announce-fewer-new-hires-in-april-challenger-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四发布的一份报告显示，美国公司在 4 月份削减了招聘计划，雇主宣布今年前四个月的新员工数量为 2016 年以来最少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/us-firms-announce-fewer-new-hires-in-april-challenger-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡星展银行 (DBS) 的数字服务在 MAS 禁令结束几天后蓬勃发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/dbs-bank-s-digital-services-hit-days-after-central-bank-ban-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，星展集团控股有限公司(DBS Group Holdings Ltd.)在新加坡的网上银行和支付服务再次受到干扰，几天前，新加坡央行因类似问题而实施的为期六个月的禁令结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/dbs-bank-s-digital-services-hit-days-after-central-bank-ban-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:53:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着交易商逃离陷入困境的市场，可可价格继续下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/cocoa-slumps-again-as-buyers-hold-back-in-troubled-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于流动性枯竭和买家不愿购买可可豆，可可价格再次暴跌，延续了一周的剧烈波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/cocoa-slumps-again-as-buyers-hold-back-in-troubled-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓首席执行官飞往南非推动 390 亿美元收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/bhp-woos-south-africa-in-pursuit-of-39-billion-anglo-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司已向南非部署了包括首席执行官在内的高级团队，这家全球最大的矿业公司正在加大努力争取政府官员、监管机构和当地股东的支持，所有这些人都可能会决定其拟议合作的结果与竞争对手英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/bhp-woos-south-africa-in-pursuit-of-39-billion-anglo-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
